Опис вакансії
A successful online financial company Clever 4ever is looking for talented and motivated English speaking sales people to join our growing team. If you don’t have experience, we will teach you !) Requirements:
Vacancy only for girls (no, we do not deal with gender discrimination, there are a lot of boys in the English-speaking department, so we want to dilute it)
Fluent English at least C1
At least full high school graduation
highly motivated and energetic
open minded
willingness to learn
previous experience in sales- an advantage
Working conditions: Comfortable office in the center Working hours: 10:00 a.m — 19:00 p.m Benefits:
$500 base salary, the best bonuses in the industry!!!(call or come for an interview and see for yourself)
official employment: paid vacation (24 calendar days per year) and paid sick leaves
medical insurance after 6 month of working with us/upgraded medical insurance after 1 year
our company has hot traffic, so you will speak with people, who are interested
Training for the English direction starts on 24.03. We consider all candidates who responded before 23.03!!!Don’t waste your time, call right now and we will arrange an interview!HR-manager Max
